      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;section-divider&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;research-areas&#34;&gt;Research Areas&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;research-area&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;research-icon&#34;&gt;&amp;#9878;&lt;/span&gt; Blockchain-Based Data Marketplaces&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p&gt;&#xA;    I design and evaluate decentralized data marketplace architectures, with a strong focus on the &lt;strong&gt;energy domain&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;    My work addresses the challenges of privacy, trust, and interoperability in data exchange, integrating&#xA;    technologies such as the Ocean Protocol, IDSA connectors, and GAIA-X dataspaces. A key result is a&#xA;    sub-8 second decentralized marketplace for energy data, demonstrating practical feasibility at scale.&#xA;  &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;tag-list&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Ocean Protocol&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;IDSA&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;GAIA-X&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Energy Data&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Digital Twins&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;research-area&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;research-icon&#34;&gt;&amp;#9881;&lt;/span&gt; DAO Governance &amp; Sustainability&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p&gt;&#xA;    I investigate &lt;strong&gt;Decentralized Autonomous Organizations (DAOs)&lt;/strong&gt; through the lens of governance sustainability&#xA;    and longevity. My work includes defining on-chain governance metrics, developing game-theoretic incentive models,&#xA;    and analyzing empirical data from existing DAOs to understand what makes decentralized governance work long-term.&#xA;  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
