      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;section-divider&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;conference-presentations&#34;&gt;Conference Presentations&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;Jul 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Paper Presentation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;Design and Evaluation of a Sub-8 Second Decentralised Marketplace for Energy Data&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE COMPSAC 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Toronto, ON, Canada&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;Jul 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Paper Presentation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;A Blockchain-Powered Digital Twin Architecture for Consumer-Centric Energy Systems&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE COMPSAC 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Toronto, ON, Canada&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;Jul 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Paper Presentation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;A Game-Theoretic Incentive Model for DAO Governance&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE COMPSAC 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Toronto, ON, Canada&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;Jul 2024&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Paper Presentation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;Shaping the Future of Energy Markets: Federated Systems and Blockchain Synergy&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE COMPSAC 2024&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Osaka, Japan&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;Oct 2023&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Paper Presentation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;Integrating a DLT-Based Data Marketplace with IDSA for a Unified Energy Dataspace&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE BRAINS 2023&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Paris, France&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;Jun 2023&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Paper Presentation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;Exploring the Potential of Energy Data Marketplaces: an Approach based on the Ocean Protocol&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE COMPSAC 2023&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Torino, Italy&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;invited-talks--seminars&#34;&gt;Invited Talks &amp;amp; Seminars&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;talk-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-date&#34;&gt;May 2025&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-type&#34;&gt;Invited Speaker&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3&gt;CrypTO SERICS Workshop&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-venue&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.polito.it/ateneo/comunicazione-e-ufficio-stampa/appuntamenti/news?idn=25869&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Politecnico di Torino&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-location&#34;&gt;Torino, Italy&lt;